Usage: unspecifyJtag [-help] {-cell <cellName> | -inst <instName> | -hinst <hinstName> | -group <cellName|hinstName>}

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cellName>                # cell name (wild card) to be made jtag cells
                                # (string, optional)
-group <cellName|hinstName>     # cell or hinst name to be made a jtag group
                                # cell (string, optional)
-hinst <hinstName>              # hinst name to be made jtag cell
                                # (string, optional)
-inst <instName>                # inst name (wild card) to be made jtag cell
                                # (string, optional)